(4536, 'Ragitovak 8mg/4ml 1 i.m./i.v./inf. amp', 'راجيتوفاك 8 مجم/4مل 1 امبولة', '', '31', 'Ondansetron', 'Hikma specialized pharmaceuticals', 'Amp', 'أمبول', '', 'Antiemetic', '8mg', 'In the adult patient population:
